Well shits and giggles.

Well its 12:21 am on August 26th. I'm supposed to be sleeping cuz I'm waking up in the morning to go to the beach. I'm getting so kick ass at my guitar. I printed 37 pages of guitar tabs at the library today lol.

More Facts About Me:

Middle name: Henry

Shoe size: 10 and a half and you know what that means... I wear big socks... what were you thinking?

Chothing Stores: Pacsun, Zumiez, Abercrombie for some dress shirts, JC Pennys, Shanghi, China (my dad is a pilot and we get like hella expensive shit for 10 bucks lol), and some other random places.

Shoes I wear: Etnies, Vans, Converse (for the gym), uh... well I have like 3 pairs of DC's, Dickies, I have some Air Force Ones I stole from the lost and found at school, Old Navy sandals, Reef sandals... and two pairs of dress shoes.

Clothes I wear I wear: Volcom, O'Niel skate clothing, DC, Kirra, Indepentent, Hurley, Adio, Etnies, North Face, Abercrombie, Bullhead, Dickies and probably some other ones too.

Bands I'm currently listening to: Blink 182, Sum 41, Weezer, Tenatious D, New Found Glory, Three Days Grace, Dashboard Confessionals, Lagwagon, some MxPx, and others (Gee I'm forgetful).

Anyways I'm bored, tired, and I need to get out. Call me on my cell 579-1019.
